<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Lesson 1 — What is Data Analytics?</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;600;700;800&family=DM+Sans:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;1,300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0a0a0f;
    --surface: #12121a;
    --surface2: #1a1a26;
    --accent: #6c63ff;
    --accent2: #ff6584;
    --accent3: #43e97b;
    --accent4: #f7971e;
    --text: #e8e8f0;
    --muted: #8888aa;
    --border: rgba(108,99,255,0.2);
  }

- { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

body {
background: var(–bg);
color: var(–text);
font-family: ‘DM Sans’, sans-serif;
font-size: 15px;
line-height: 1.7;
min-height: 100vh;
overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* Ambient background */
body::before {
content: ‘’;
position: fixed;
top: -200px; left: -200px;
width: 600px; height: 600px;
background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(108,99,255,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
pointer-events: none;
z-index: 0;
}
body::after {
content: ‘’;
position: fixed;
bottom: -200px; right: -200px;
width: 500px; height: 500px;
background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,101,132,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
pointer-events: none;
z-index: 0;
}

.page {
max-width: 860px;
margin: 0 auto;
padding: 48px 24px 80px;
position: relative;
z-index: 1;
}

/* Header */
.course-tag {
display: inline-flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 8px;
background: rgba(108,99,255,0.15);
border: 1px solid var(–border);
border-radius: 100px;
padding: 6px 16px;
font-size: 12px;
font-weight: 500;
color: var(–accent);
letter-spacing: 0.08em;
text-transform: uppercase;
margin-bottom: 28px;
animation: fadeDown 0.6s ease both;
}
.course-tag::before {
content: ‘’;
width: 6px; height: 6px;
background: var(–accent);
border-radius: 50%;
animation: pulse 2s infinite;
}

@keyframes pulse {
0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
50% { opacity: 0.3; }
}

.lesson-title {
font-family: ‘Syne’, sans-serif;
font-size: clamp(32px, 6vw, 52px);
font-weight: 800;
line-height: 1.1;
margin-bottom: 12px;
animation: fadeDown 0.6s 0.1s ease both;
}
.lesson-title span {
background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(–accent), var(–accent2));
-webkit-background-clip: text;
-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
background-clip: text;
}

.lesson-subtitle {
color: var(–muted);
font-size: 16px;
margin-bottom: 48px;
animation: fadeDown 0.6s 0.2s ease both;
}

/* Section label */
.section-label {
font-size: 11px;
font-weight: 600;
letter-spacing: 0.15em;
text-transform: uppercase;
color: var(–accent);
margin-bottom: 16px;
display: flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 10px;
}
.section-label::after {
content: ‘’;
flex: 1;
height: 1px;
background: var(–border);
}

/* Definition card */
.definition-card {
background: var(–surface);
border: 1px solid var(–border);
border-radius: 20px;
padding: 32px;
margin-bottom: 40px;
position: relative;
overflow: hidden;
animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.3s ease both;
}
.definition-card::before {
content: ‘”’;
position: absolute;
top: -20px; right: 20px;
font-size: 160px;
font-family: ‘Syne’, sans-serif;
color: rgba(108,99,255,0.06);
line-height: 1;
pointer-events: none;
}
.definition-card p {
font-size: 18px;
font-weight: 300;
line-height: 1.8;
color: var(–text);
}
.definition-card p strong {
color: #fff;
font-weight: 500;
}

/* Analogy box */
.analogy {
background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(108,99,255,0.12), rgba(255,101,132,0.08));
border: 1px solid rgba(108,99,255,0.3);
border-radius: 16px;
padding: 24px 28px;
margin-bottom: 40px;
animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.4s ease both;
}
.analogy-title {
font-family: ‘Syne’, sans-serif;
font-weight: 700;
font-size: 13px;
letter-spacing: 0.1em;
text-transform: uppercase;
color: var(–accent2);
margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.analogy p { font-size: 15px; color: var(–text); }
.analogy p em { color: var(–accent2); font-style: normal; font-weight: 500; }

/* Role cards - what analyst does */
.role-grid {
display: grid;
grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
gap: 16px;
margin-bottom: 48px;
animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.5s ease both;
}

.role-card {
background: var(–surface);
border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
border-radius: 16px;
padding: 24px 20px;
position: relative;
overflow: hidden;
transition: transform 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
}
.role-card:hover {
transform: translateY(-3px);
border-color: rgba(108,99,255,0.4);
}
.role-card::after {
content: ‘’;
position: absolute;
bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
height: 2px;
background: var(–card-color);
opacity: 0.6;
}

.role-number {
font-family: ‘Syne’, sans-serif;
font-size: 36px;
font-weight: 800;
color: var(–card-color);
opacity: 0.3;
line-height: 1;
margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.role-verb {
font-family: ‘Syne’, sans-serif;
font-size: 18px;
font-weight: 700;
color: var(–card-color);
margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.role-desc {
font-size: 13px;
color: var(–muted);
line-height: 1.5;
}

/* Analytics types */
.types-section { margin-bottom: 48px; animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.6s ease both; }

.types-grid {
display: grid;
grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
gap: 14px;
}

@media (max-width: 540px) {
.types-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}

.type-card {
background: var(–surface);
border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
border-radius: 16px;
padding: 22px 20px;
display: flex;
gap: 16px;
align-items: flex-start;
transition: transform 0.2s;
}
.type-card:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }

.type-icon {
width: 44px; height: 44px;
border-radius: 12px;
display: flex;
align-items: center;
justify-content: center;
font-size: 20px;
flex-shrink: 0;
}

.type-content {}
.type-name {
font-family: ‘Syne’, sans-serif;
font-weight: 700;
font-size: 15px;
margin-bottom: 2px;
color: #fff;
}
.type-question {
font-size: 12px;
color: var(–accent);
margin-bottom: 6px;
font-weight: 500;
}
.type-example {
font-size: 12px;
color: var(–muted);
line-height: 1.5;
font-style: italic;
}

/* Process flow */
.process-section { margin-bottom: 48px; animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.7s ease both; }

.process-flow {
display: flex;
flex-wrap: wrap;
gap: 0;
background: var(–surface);
border: 1px solid var(–border);
border-radius: 20px;
overflow: hidden;
}

.process-step {
flex: 1;
min-width: 100px;
padding: 24px 16px;
text-align: center;
position: relative;
border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
transition: background 0.2s;
}
.process-step:last-child { border-right: none; }
.process-step:hover { background: rgba(108,99,255,0.08); }

.process-emoji { font-size: 26px; margin-bottom: 8px; display: block; }
.process-name {
font-family: ‘Syne’, sans-serif;
font-weight: 700;
font-size: 13px;
color: #fff;
margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.process-q {
font-size: 11px;
color: var(–muted);
line-height: 1.4;
}

@media (max-width: 600px) {
.process-flow { flex-direction: column; }
.process-step { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }
.process-step:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
}

/* Real world example */
.real-world {
background: var(–surface);
border: 1px solid rgba(67,233,123,0.2);
border-radius: 20px;
padding: 28px 32px;
margin-bottom: 40px;
animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.8s ease both;
}
.real-world-title {
display: flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 10px;
font-family: ‘Syne’, sans-serif;
font-weight: 700;
font-size: 16px;
color: var(–accent3);
margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.example-row {
display: flex;
gap: 12px;
margin-bottom: 10px;
align-items: flex-start;
}
.example-badge {
font-size: 11px;
font-weight: 600;
letter-spacing: 0.08em;
padding: 3px 10px;
border-radius: 100px;
white-space: nowrap;
flex-shrink: 0;
margin-top: 2px;
}
.badge-desc { background: rgba(108,99,255,0.2); color: var(–accent); }
.badge-diag { background: rgba(247,151,30,0.2); color: var(–accent4); }
.badge-pred { background: rgba(255,101,132,0.2); color: var(–accent2); }
.badge-pres { background: rgba(67,233,123,0.2); color: var(–accent3); }
.example-text { font-size: 14px; color: var(–text); }

/* Toolkit */
.toolkit-section { margin-bottom: 48px; animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.9s ease both; }

.toolkit-grid {
display: grid;
grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
gap: 12px;
}
@media (max-width: 540px) { .toolkit-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }

.tool-card {
background: var(–surface);
border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
border-radius: 14px;
padding: 18px 16px;
text-align: center;
transition: transform 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
}
.tool-card:hover {
transform: translateY(-3px);
border-color: rgba(108,99,255,0.35);
}
.tool-emoji { font-size: 28px; display: block; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.tool-name {
font-family: ‘Syne’, sans-serif;
font-weight: 700;
font-size: 14px;
color: #fff;
margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.tool-why { font-size: 11px; color: var(–muted); line-height: 1.4; }

/* Homework */
.homework {
background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(247,151,30,0.1), rgba(255,101,132,0.06));
border: 1px solid rgba(247,151,30,0.25);
border-radius: 20px;
padding: 28px 32px;
margin-bottom: 40px;
animation: fadeUp 0.7s 1s ease both;
}
.homework-title {
font-family: ‘Syne’, sans-serif;
font-weight: 700;
font-size: 16px;
color: var(–accent4);
margin-bottom: 16px;
display: flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 10px;
}
.hw-item {
display: flex;
gap: 12px;
margin-bottom: 12px;
align-items: flex-start;
}
.hw-num {
width: 24px; height: 24px;
background: rgba(247,151,30,0.2);
border-radius: 50%;
display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: var(–accent4);
flex-shrink: 0;
}
.hw-text { font-size: 14px; color: var(–text); line-height: 1.6; }
.hw-text em { color: var(–accent4); font-style: normal; }

/* Bottom nav */
.bottom-nav {
display: flex;
align-items: center;
justify-content: space-between;
border-top: 1px solid var(–border);
padding-top: 28px;
animation: fadeUp 0.7s 1.1s ease both;
}
.nav-info { font-size: 13px; color: var(–muted); }
.nav-next {
display: inline-flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 8px;
background: var(–accent);
color: #fff;
border: none;
border-radius: 100px;
padding: 12px 24px;
font-family: ‘Syne’, sans-serif;
font-weight: 700;
font-size: 14px;
cursor: pointer;
transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
}
.nav-next:hover {
transform: translateY(-2px);
box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(108,99,255,0.4);
}

/* Animations */
@keyframes fadeDown {
from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-16px); }
to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}
@keyframes fadeUp {
from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

/* Progress bar */
.progress-bar {
position: fixed;
top: 0; left: 0;
height: 3px;
background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(–accent), var(–accent2));
width: 5%;
transition: width 0.3s;
z-index: 999;
}
</style>

</head>
<body>

<div class="progress-bar" id="progressBar"></div>

<div class="page">

  <div class="course-tag">Phase 1 · Week 1 · Lesson 1</div>

  <h1 class="lesson-title">What is<br><span>Data Analytics?</span></h1>
  <p class="lesson-subtitle">Your first step into one of the most in-demand careers of the decade.</p>

  <!-- Definition -->

  <div class="section-label">The Core Idea</div>
  <div class="definition-card">
    <p>Data Analytics is the process of <strong>examining raw data</strong> to find patterns, draw conclusions, and help people make <strong>better decisions</strong>. It turns a pile of numbers into a clear story that anyone can act on.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Analogy -->

  <div class="analogy">
    <div class="analogy-title">🧠 Think of it this way</div>
    <p>A data analyst is like a <em>detective for business problems</em>. The data is your crime scene. Your job is to find clues, connect the dots, and tell the world what actually happened — and what to do next.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- What does an analyst do -->

  <div class="section-label">What a Data Analyst Actually Does</div>
  <div class="role-grid">
    <div class="role-card" style="--card-color: #6c63ff;">
      <div class="role-number">01</div>
      <div class="role-verb">Collect</div>
      <div class="role-desc">Gather data from databases, spreadsheets, APIs, and reports</div>
    </div>
    <div class="role-card" style="--card-color: #ff6584;">
      <div class="role-number">02</div>
      <div class="role-verb">Clean</div>
      <div class="role-desc">Fix errors, remove duplicates, handle missing values</div>
    </div>
    <div class="role-card" style="--card-color: #f7971e;">
      <div class="role-number">03</div>
      <div class="role-verb">Analyze</div>
      <div class="role-desc">Find patterns, trends, and outliers in the data</div>
    </div>
    <div class="role-card" style="--card-color: #43e97b;">
      <div class="role-number">04</div>
      <div class="role-verb">Visualize</div>
      <div class="role-desc">Turn numbers into charts, graphs, and dashboards</div>
    </div>
    <div class="role-card" style="--card-color: #38b2ff;">
      <div class="role-number">05</div>
      <div class="role-verb">Recommend</div>
      <div class="role-desc">Present insights and suggest actions to stakeholders</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 4 Types -->

  <div class="types-section">
    <div class="section-label">4 Types of Analytics</div>
    <div class="types-grid">
      <div class="type-card">
        <div class="type-icon" style="background:rgba(108,99,255,0.15);">📊</div>
        <div class="type-content">
          <div class="type-name">Descriptive</div>
          <div class="type-question">What happened?</div>
          <div class="type-example">"We processed 500 orders last month"</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="type-card">
        <div class="type-icon" style="background:rgba(247,151,30,0.15);">🔍</div>
        <div class="type-content">
          <div class="type-name">Diagnostic</div>
          <div class="type-question">Why did it happen?</div>
          <div class="type-example">"Orders dropped due to approval delays"</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="type-card">
        <div class="type-icon" style="background:rgba(255,101,132,0.15);">🔮</div>
        <div class="type-content">
          <div class="type-name">Predictive</div>
          <div class="type-question">What will happen?</div>
          <div class="type-example">"Next quarter orders will rise 15%"</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="type-card">
        <div class="type-icon" style="background:rgba(67,233,123,0.15);">⚡</div>
        <div class="type-content">
          <div class="type-name">Prescriptive</div>
          <div class="type-question">What should we do?</div>
          <div class="type-example">"Automate approvals to cut delays"</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Process Flow -->

  <div class="process-section">
    <div class="section-label">The Analytics Process — Every Single Time</div>
    <div class="process-flow">
      <div class="process-step">
        <span class="process-emoji">❓</span>
        <div class="process-name">Ask</div>
        <div class="process-q">Define the problem</div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <span class="process-emoji">📥</span>
        <div class="process-name">Collect</div>
        <div class="process-q">Get the data</div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <span class="process-emoji">🧹</span>
        <div class="process-name">Clean</div>
        <div class="process-q">Fix the mess</div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <span class="process-emoji">🔬</span>
        <div class="process-name">Analyze</div>
        <div class="process-q">Find patterns</div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <span class="process-emoji">📈</span>
        <div class="process-name">Visualize</div>
        <div class="process-q">Tell the story</div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <span class="process-emoji">🚀</span>
        <div class="process-name">Act</div>
        <div class="process-q">Drive decisions</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Real world from his job -->

  <div class="real-world">
    <div class="real-world-title">🏢 Real Example — From Your World at Curriculum Associates</div>
    <div class="example-row">
      <span class="example-badge badge-desc">Descriptive</span>
      <span class="example-text">"How many license orders were processed in Q3 across all school districts?"</span>
    </div>
    <div class="example-row">
      <span class="example-badge badge-diag">Diagnostic</span>
      <span class="example-text">"Why did processing time spike in November? Was it SAP delays or approval bottlenecks?"</span>
    </div>
    <div class="example-row">
      <span class="example-badge badge-pred">Predictive</span>
      <span class="example-text">"Based on last year's pattern, which months will see the highest order volume?"</span>
    </div>
    <div class="example-row">
      <span class="example-badge badge-pres">Prescriptive</span>
      <span class="example-text">"We should add temporary processing staff in Oct–Nov to handle the predicted surge."</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Toolkit -->

  <div class="toolkit-section">
    <div class="section-label">Your Full Toolkit — What You'll Learn</div>
    <div class="toolkit-grid">
      <div class="tool-card">
        <span class="tool-emoji">📗</span>
        <div class="tool-name">Excel</div>
        <div class="tool-why">Universal. Every company uses it. Your first weapon.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="tool-card">
        <span class="tool-emoji">🗄️</span>
        <div class="tool-name">SQL</div>
        <div class="tool-why">Talk to databases. Most in-demand skill in analytics.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="tool-card">
        <span class="tool-emoji">🐍</span>
        <div class="tool-name">Python</div>
        <div class="tool-why">Automate analysis, handle large datasets.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="tool-card">
        <span class="tool-emoji">📊</span>
        <div class="tool-name">Power BI</div>
        <div class="tool-why">Build dashboards. Huge demand in Indian market.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="tool-card">
        <span class="tool-emoji">🎨</span>
        <div class="tool-name">Tableau</div>
        <div class="tool-why">Visual storytelling. Popular in MNCs.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="tool-card">
        <span class="tool-emoji">📐</span>
        <div class="tool-name">Statistics</div>
        <div class="tool-why">Think analytically, not just technically.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Homework -->

  <div class="homework">
    <div class="homework-title">✏️ Week 1 Homework</div>
    <div class="hw-item">
      <div class="hw-num">1</div>
      <div class="hw-text">Think of <em>3 questions</em> you wish you could answer with data from your current job</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hw-item">
      <div class="hw-num">2</div>
      <div class="hw-text">Write one question for each type: <em>Descriptive</em>, <em>Diagnostic</em>, and <em>Prescriptive</em></div>
    </div>
    <div class="hw-item">
      <div class="hw-num">3</div>
      <div class="hw-text">Example: <em>"How many orders were delayed last month? Why? Should we hire more staff?"</em></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Bottom nav -->

  <div class="bottom-nav">
    <div class="nav-info">Phase 1 · Week 1 · Lesson 1 of 1</div>
    <button class="nav-next" onclick="alert('Say \'Next\' in the chat to continue to Lesson 2!')">
      Next Lesson →
    </button>
  </div>

</div>

<script>
  // Progress bar on scroll
  window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
    const scrolled = window.scrollY;
    const total = document.body.scrollHeight - window.innerHeight;
    const pct = Math.min(100, 5 + (scrolled / total) * 95);
    document.getElementById('progressBar').style.width = pct + '%';
  });
</script>

</body>
</html>